  <brief_title>Hemcon© Bandage for Postpartum Bleeding Due to the Multiple Vaginal Lacerations</brief_title>
  <official_title>THE EFFICACY AND SAFETY OF HEMCON© BANDAGE FOLLOWING SURGICAL REPAIR IN MANAGEMENT OF POSTPARTUM BLEEDING DUE TO THE MULTIPLE VAGINAL LACERATIONS</official_title>
