  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to assess the safety and efficacy of the HemCon GuardaCareXR
      compared to standard bandaging in subjects with post partum hemorrhage as a result of
      cervical and vaginal lacerations. The primary endpoint will be a cessation of bleeding at 30
      minutes after insertion of the dressing.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
